body:
SkyConsult is looking for a SAP SD Consultant with hands on experience in 2nd Level Support for Sales and Distribution related issues escalated by the 1st Level Support team of our client.

Blueprint of typical tasks:

He/she will:
>  assist the customer in adopting the best solutions to adapt SAP environment to actual business requirements;
> perform the analysis, configuration and implementation of the minor changes or change requests approved by the customer.
> make use of consulting skills, business processes knowledge and SAP solution expertise to provide efficient support and integrate SAP technology into the client’s complex business environment.

Required Job skill set:
>  support, design, configuration and testing of core SAP Sales and Distribution modules;
>  experience and knowledge of key integration points of Sales and Distribution, Logistics modules with other SAP modules:
>  successful implementation of SAP, including providing functional expertise, guidance, presentation, training and support activities on SAP products;  
> inventiveness, ability to find fast and smart solutions in existing SAP environment to incidents or customer’s requirements;
> customer management experience and concern;
>  excellent communication skills;
> business knowledge and process design skills;
> Bachelor's Degree
> minimum 5 years of SAP SD / Logistics Execution configuration/support experience
> fluency in written and spoken English;
> knowledge of SAP IS-Oil & Gas functionalities - nice to have;
> SAP Idoc and interfaces experience - nice to have.
